## ðŸ“Œ What is Appwrite?

* Appwrite is an **open-source Backend-as-a-Service (BaaS)** platform
* Provides ready-made backend services
* Used to build apps faster without writing backend from scratch
* Alternative to Firebase (open-source & self-hosted)

---

## ðŸ§  Why Appwrite?

* No need to build authentication manually
* Built-in database & storage
* Secure by default
* Works well with frontend frameworks (React, Next.js, Flutter)

---

## ðŸ§© Core Appwrite Services

### ðŸ” Authentication

